* UI pieces for components are sent from the component through the manager
  to the admin client.

* admin client:
  - asks for the md5sum of the UI zipfile.
  - checks if it has it
  - requests the zipfile if it doesn't
  - unpacks in (md5sum)/
  - runs code in it

* component:
  - gets request for md5sum of UI zipfile
  - checks timestamp on each of the files to go into the zipfile
  - if any outdated, rebuild zipfile, and load it in memory
  - md5sum it
  - send md5sum

  - gets request for zipfile
  - sends zipfile

